\": 354, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"lesser supported sports\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here atCity A.M.we have broken where the value is, and where can you get bang for your buck in comparison to the size and status of the various events at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"atCity\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 406}, {\"ngram\": \"A.M.we\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"the value\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"bang\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"your buck\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"status\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the various events\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the showpiece event of any Olympic Games, where the fastest men in the world compete for glory.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the showpiece event\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"any Olympic Games\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest men\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The iconic Stade de France will host this year's final with tickets for the evening session on Sunday 4 August ranging from \\u00a3245 in Category C to \\u00a3820 at Category A.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The iconic Stade de France\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening session\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"Category C\", \"from\": 797,